\section{@Delft3D\_His}
\subsection{Delft3D\_His}
${}$
\begin{lstlisting}
			fdx = (Xc~=0) & (Yc~=0);
			fdx(1,:) = true; fdx(end,:) = true;
			fdx(:,1) = true; fdx(:,end) = true;
			fdx = fdx & (X>0);
			X = obj.X;
			for idx=1:size(u3,2)
			 % first
			 if (isnan(u3(1,idx,1,1)))
				u3(:,idx,1,:) = 0;
			 end % if first
			 % centre
			 for jdx=2:size(u3,3)-1
				if (~isnan(X(idx,jdx)) && isnan(u3(1,idx,jdx,1)) ...
				     && ( isnan(X(idx,jdx+1)) || isnan(X(idx,jdx-1)) ) )
					u3(:,idx,jdx,:) = 0;
				end
			 end % for jdx
			 % last
			 if (isnan(u3(1,idx,end,1)))
				u3(:,idx,end,:) = 0;
			 end % if last
			end % for idx

\end{lstlisting}
